  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK570">
<l>kallārp piṇikkuṅ kaṭuṅkō latuvalla </l>
<l> tillai nilakkup poṟai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The earth bears up no greater burden than ignorant men whom a cruel sceptre attaches to itself (as the ministers of its evil deeds).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
